title: Watchmen Portfolio (1988)
description:
'Watchmen Portfolio'
DC Comics, 1988, 32 pages
Illustrated by Dave Gibbons (I think)

This is a Watchmen art portfolio from 1988. It features the six French Watchmen covers (that I'm not sure were done by Gibbons - they have no signature), six promotional posters and the original twelve U.S. covers. Probably only for the hardcore Watchmen completists, but it's a vibrant, high quality scan of something I'd never seen before so I thought I;d pass it along.
